2003-12-04  Dave Morrison  <dmrrsn@users.sourceforge.net>

	* Makefile, fink.info.in: Modification of strategy for running the
	test suite.  We now check for the presence of Test::More before
	invoking the tests.  This will fail during bootstrap under 10.2
	but will work at other times.  (Avoids the problems of introducing
	new packages as essential.)

2003-12-04  Dave Morrison  <dmrrsn@users.sourceforge.net>

	* fink.info.in, bootstrap.pl: Run the test suite while building
	fink.  (Requires new bootstrap packages file-spec-pm, test-simple-pm, 
	and test-harness-pm when running under perl 5.6.x.)

